{"tid":2507094,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察」呢個職業係咪有BUG?","createTime":"2021-04-27T19:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T05:25:51.000Z","uid":275912,"like":693,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"15adf8257d672e27e1891898a977922be7cea4bd","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:14:44.000Z","msg":"香港啲狗就唔駛講啦<br />\n今日睇台灣節目講左兩單新聞<br />\n<br />\n1.有個警察飲完酒亂屌人屌中黑社會<br />\n黑社會衝入警局搗亂<br />\n但黑社會無後果走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過左四五日先有基層警察爆料<br />\n再經媒體報導越鬧越大<br />\n要求拎警局CCTV，局長話停電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後發現係局長刪左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(望向黨鐵)<br />\n跟住內部處分吓，同相關黑社會握手和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.一位市民行行吓比警察截查<br />\n問咩名呀，住邊咁樣<br />\n個市民覺得佢無禮貌唔理佢想走<br />\n比警察過肩摔<br />\n再叫支援，上手扣比三個警察押上車<br />\n去到警局仲上埋腳鐐，唔比掂自己物品，困左九個鐘<br />\nPS.呢單響香港就好小事姐，截查一定要合作<br />\n唔合作佢鐘意點玩都得，點玩都係你唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPSS.有冇人清楚台灣果邊，截查有冇相關規例?<br />\n<br />\n「警察」權力過大，無監管，好似好多國家都有咁既情況<br />\n到底係咪有BUG?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全世界「黑」警死全家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地都係打份工，壞警察只係一小撮"},{"pid":"342d7d98a10489bb085cd830b8b21c33398696c1","tid":2507094,"uid":142247,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:27:10.000Z","msg":"權力使人腐敗"},{"pid":"01abfd6f2abedbcedc966f4472c6435bc2bf2fad","tid":2507094,"uid":54256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:29:29.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"c5da9a52e31e4de543756c0282a2c8751684319e","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":8,"disl