到well educated,有良好道德觀既人<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，一隻狗無啦啦咬傷人，主人平時既教育都好有問題，你唔會期望隻狗有人類既道德觀/情緒控制<br />\n<br />\n狗好得意，係人類既朋友<br />\n香港差佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb14495f8fa3c6655ec2a3353ec8ff12cbe99c7d","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c3311ea0acfaad1547a4713805442710a880bf","tid":2507094,"uid":131125,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"944e1ced9ff6b9bec5fbb1c2aea4472ecb37fd64","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T20:10:29.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個國家<br />\n可以有效監察/限制警察既權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nICAC唔算<br />\n佢地只係睇貪污<br />\n而家更加只係飲咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T20:51:11.000Z","msg":"美國咁囉<br />\n跪完頸真係有判刑<br />\n但點平衡都係事後嘅野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當下有權有槍真係無撚敵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"如果無上新聞<br />\n仲會唔會有人追究?<br />\n仲需唔需要接受法律懲罰?<br />\n<br />\n1樓既例子2<br />\n當事人自己都講<br />\n如果當時無人幫佢影低<br />\n可能都係口同鼻拗"},{"pid":"450267beec8848a93d04f2eb41264caa45045ad9","tid":2507094,"uid":336670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"所以我希望現實世界好似D dystopia電影, 會有機械人警察, 前題係個progamme唔會比政府完全控制, 會有一堆logical rules去分析行動, 冇bias"},{"pid":"75170bc7d12859f704195fb9cfdee693b9044711","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"280e93d7df1e0b4b39f16c6b4bccc61a6d3d4e36","tid":2507094,"uid":38121,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"10c3311ea0acfaad1547a4713805442710a880bf","tid":2507094,"uid":131125,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"944e1ced9ff6b9bec5fbb1c2aea4472ecb37fd64","tid":2507094,"uid":275912,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T20:10:29.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個國家<br />\n可以有效監察/限制警察既權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"